Community



Complete the form below to submit your information for a public member profile on the RC42 Social Psychology portal.




&lt;p&gt;This form collects information exclusively for the RC42 members directory. It is &lt;strong&gt;separate&lt;/strong&gt; from official ISA membership registration. Your data will be reviewed by the board prior to publication.&lt;/p&gt;



Don’t fill this out: 


Required Information

Full name * 
Email for verification * 

Used for verification only. It will not be published unless you explicitly provide a public email below.

Primary Affiliation * 
Country * 
Short Biography *

Research Interests *

Relationship with RC42 *  – Select your status – Current ISA RC42 member Former ISA RC42 member Interested in joining RC42 Collaborator / affiliated scholar Other 

Optional Information

City 
Photo URL 

Provide a URL to a professional photo. Alternatively, you can email a photo to the board after submission.

ORCID 
Google Scholar 
LinkedIn 
Personal Website 
Public Email 
Selected Publications


Consent & Submission


&lt;div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"&gt;
  &lt;input type="checkbox" id="consent-publish" name="consent-publish" required&gt;
  &lt;label for="consent-publish"&gt;I consent to have my profile information published on the RC42 Social Psychology portal. &lt;span class="required-mark"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;input type="checkbox" id="consent-store" name="consent-store" required&gt;
  &lt;label for="consent-store"&gt;I consent to having this submission stored for editorial review by the RC42 board. &lt;span class="required-mark"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;button type="submit" class="btn-rc42-primary"&gt;Submit Profile for Review&lt;/button&gt;
